{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":982,"text":"This is where I live. I live in Kenya,"},{"time":3756,"text":"at the south parts of the Nairobi National Park."},{"time":6823,"text":"Those are my dad's cows at the back,"},{"time":8811,"text":"and behind the cows,"},{"time":10791,"text":"that's the Nairobi National Park."},{"time":13095,"text":"Nairobi National Park is not fenced in the south widely,"},{"time":16600,"text":"which means wild animals like zebras"},{"time":20062,"text":"migrate out of the park freely."},{"time":23983,"text":"So predators like lions follow them,"},{"time":27996,"text":"and this is what they do."},{"time":30791,"text":"They kill our livestock."},{"time":33792,"text":"This is one of the cows which was killed at night,"},{"time":36239,"text":"and I just woke up in the morning and I found it dead,"},{"time":40279,"text":"and I felt so bad,"},{"time":42705,"text":"because it was the only bull we had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47192,"text":"My community, the Maasai, we believe that"},{"time":49979,"text":"we came from heaven with all our animals and all the land"},{"time":56036,"text":"for herding them, and that's why we value them so much."},{"time":59811,"text":"So I grew up hating lions so much."},{"time":63570,"text":"The morans are the warriors"},{"time":66623,"text":"who protect our community and the livestock,"},{"time":69940,"text":"and they're also upset about this problem."},{"time":73019,"text":"So they kill the lions."},{"time":76024,"text":"It's one of the six lions which were killed in Nairobi."},{"time":79938,"text":"And I think this is why the Nairobi National Park lions are few."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84477,"text":"So a boy, from six to nine years old, in my community"},{"time":89438,"text":"is responsible for his dad's cows,"},{"time":92312,"text":"and that's the same thing which happened to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95442,"text":"So I had to find a way of solving this problem."},{"time":98857,"text":"And the first idea I got was to use fire,"},{"time":103671,"text":"because I thought lions were scared of fire."},{"time":107464,"text":"But I came to realize that that didn't really help,"},{"time":112183,"text":"because it was even helping the lions"},{"time":114792,"text":"to see through the cowshed."},{"time":118303,"text":"So I didn't give up. I continued."},{"time":121632,"text":"And a second idea I got was"},{"time":124272,"text":"to use a scarecrow."},{"time":126339,"text":"I was trying to trick the lions"},{"time":127953,"text":"[into thinking] that I was standing near the cowshed."},{"time":130860,"text":"But lions are very clever. (Laughter)"},{"time":134936,"text":"They will come the first day and they see the scarecrow, and they go back,"},{"time":139382,"text":"but the second day, they'll come and they say,"},{"time":142656,"text":"this thing is not moving here, it's always here. (Laughter)"},{"time":145766,"text":"So he jumps in and kills the animals."},{"time":149003,"text":"So one night, I was walking around the cowshed with a torch,"},{"time":152956,"text":"and that day, the lions didn't come."},{"time":156799,"text":"And I discovered that lions are afraid of a moving light."},{"time":161357,"text":"So I had an idea."},{"time":163930,"text":"Since I was a small boy,"},{"time":166240,"text":"I used to work in my room for the whole day,"},{"time":169498,"text":"and I even took apart my mom's new radio,"},{"time":172604,"text":"and that day she almost killed me,"},{"time":174422,"text":"but I learned a lot about electronics. (Laughter)"},{"time":180676,"text":"So I got an old car battery,"},{"time":184036,"text":"an indicator box. It's a small device found in a motorcycle,"},{"time":187826,"text":"and it helps motorists when they want to turn right or left. It blinks."},{"time":192877,"text":"And I got a switch where I can switch on the lights, on and off."},{"time":197431,"text":"And that's a small torch from a broken flashlight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202259,"text":"So I set up everything."},{"time":205140,"text":"As you can see, the solar panel charges the battery,"},{"time":208364,"text":"and the battery supplies the power"},{"time":210485,"text":"to the small indicator box. I call it a transformer."},{"time":213540,"text":"And the indicator box makes the lights flash."},{"time":218261,"text":"As you can see, the bulbs face outside,"},{"time":222012,"text":"because that's where the lions come from."},{"time":224500,"text":"And that's how it looks to lions when they come at night."},{"time":228564,"text":"The lights flash and trick"},{"time":231292,"text":"the lions into thinking I was walking around the cowshed,"},{"time":233234,"text":"but I was sleeping in my bed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235160,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":237900,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":239569,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245164,"text":"So I set it up in my home two years ago,"},{"time":249440,"text":"and since then, we have never experienced any problem with lions."},{"time":252760,"text":"And my neighboring homes heard about this idea."},{"time":256772,"text":"One of them was this grandmother."},{"time":259236,"text":"She had a lot of her animals being killed by lions,"},{"time":263512,"text":"and she asked me if I could put the lights for her."},{"time":265646,"text":"And I said, \"Yes.\""},{"time":266924,"text":"So I put the lights. You can see at the back, those are the lion lights."},{"time":271524,"text":"Since now, I've set up seven homes around my community,"},{"time":274940,"text":"and they're really working."},{"time":277165,"text":"And my idea is also being used now all over Kenya"},{"time":282345,"text":"for scaring other predators like hyenas, leopards,"},{"time":287458,"text":"and it's also being used"},{"time":289693,"text":"to scare elephants away from people's farms."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293738,"text":"Because of this invention, I was lucky to get a scholarship"},{"time":296778,"text":"in one of the best schools in Kenya,"},{"time":299428,"text":"Brookhouse International School,"},{"time":301335,"text":"and I'm really excited about this."},{"time":304262,"text":"My new school now is coming in and helping"},{"time":308112,"text":"by fundraising and creating an awareness."},{"time":312644,"text":"I even took my friends back to my community,"},{"time":317927,"text":"and we're installing the lights to the homes"},{"time":321124,"text":"which don't have [any], and I'm teaching them how to put them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325773,"text":"So one year ago, I was just a boy in the savanna grassland"},{"time":329670,"text":"herding my father's cows,"},{"time":331344,"text":"and I used to see planes flying over,"},{"time":334298,"text":"and I told myself that one day, I'll be there inside."},{"time":338509,"text":"And here I am today."},{"time":341597,"text":"I got a chance to come by plane for my first time for TED."},{"time":347533,"text":"So my big dream is to become an aircraft engineer and pilot when I grow up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352969,"text":"I used to hate lions, but now because my invention"},{"time":356663,"text":"is saving my father's cows and the lions,"},{"time":359981,"text":"we are able to stay with the lions without any conflict."},{"time":363681,"text":"Ashê olên. It means in my language, thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366901,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":381381,"text":"Chris Anderson: You have no idea how exciting it is"},{"time":383682,"text":"to hear a story like yours."},{"time":385793,"text":"So you got this scholarship.Richard Turere: Yep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387829,"text":"CA: You're working on other electrical inventions."},{"time":390406,"text":"What's the next one on your list?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":392264,"text":"RT: My next invention is,"},{"time":394938,"text":"I want to make an electric fence.CA: Electric fence?"},{"time":397520,"text":"RT: But I know electric fences are already invented,"},{"time":399681,"text":"but I want to make mine."},{"time":401918,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":404009,"text":"CA: You already tried it once, right, and you --RT: I tried it before,"},{"time":407179,"text":"but I stopped because it gave me a shock. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":413936,"text":"CA: In the trenches. Richard Turere, you are something else."},{"time":417262,"text":"We're going to cheer you on every step of the way, my friend."},{"time":420230,"text":"Thank you so much.RT: Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}